description:
Attempt to snatch something from an enemy.
Success chance goes up with enemy distraction.
name: Steal
move
note:
<Custom User Row>
if (row > 1) {
row = 1;
} else {
row = 2;
}
</Custom User Row>

description: Reveal an enemy's info and items that you couldn't normally steal. Close range only.
name: Scan

description: Drop a bomb from high overhead. Raises Distraction and may inflict Berserk.
name: Drop Payload

description: Removes buffs and adds random statuses to all enemies. Only usable from above.
name: Chemtrail

description: Close-range electrical surge. Hurts the user and frightens the target.
name: Assault & Batteries

description: Your sweet song draws everyone's attention.
name: COME HITHER

description: Your hatred and hunger for battle grant everyone random bonuses.
name: WAR GOD'S BLESSING

description: Take hits for an ally above you and grant them 20 Hatred.
name: CHAMPION HATRED
note:
<Row Only: 1>
<Back Row Only>
<After Eval>
   user.addState(19);
</After Eval>

description: Descend to distract and frighten the enemy.
name: BATTLE CHARGE

description: Commit murder most fowl. Works on everything always.
name: Murder

description: Blind an enemy, lowering their accuracy.
message1: brings down a veil of ultimate darkness!
name: Curse of Darkness

description: Silence an enemy, preventing many abilities.
name: Nevermore

description: Frighten an enemy, with a chance to cut down their defenses.
name: Sharpen Knife

description: Frighten all enemies, and then high-tail it out of battle.
name: Retch & Run

description: Take a bite out of an enemy, inflicting fear and restoring some hunger.
name: Gorge

description: Begin circling an enemy, causing them fear every turn for 3 turns.
name: Demonic Circle

description: The next hit to this bird will deal 1 damage.
name: Desert Mirage

description: Descend toward the enemy and frighten them.
name: Divebomb

description: Take flight, distracting all enemies with the roar of your engine.
name: Takeoff

description: Let an ally in the sky with you fly behind you for a speed boost.
name: Tailwind

description: Raise an enemy's Fear by half of their Distraction.
name: Wakeup Call

description: Insure yourself and get 5 Shiny next time you take damage.
message1: takes out a life insurance policy!
name: Insurance Policy

description: Pay the enemy 10 Shiny to look the other way, raising their Distraction.
name: Bribery
note:
<Custom Requirement>
   if ($gameParty.gold() > 10) {
     value = true;
   } else {
     value = false;
   }
</Custom Requirement>

<Custom Execution>
   $gameParty.loseGold(10);
</Custom Execution>

description: Spend 5 Shiny to buy a random item.
name: Purchase
note:
<Custom Requirement>
   if ($gameParty.gold() > 10) {
     value = true;
   } else {
     value = false;
   }
</Custom Requirement>

<Custom Execution>
   $gameParty.loseGold(10);
</Custom Execution>

<Post-Damage Eval>
   $gameTemp.reserveCommonEvent(2);
</Post-Damage Eval>
